<div class="panel article-item">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h4 id="Article-58372">Salford partnership scoops special ‘vanguard’ status</h4>
<div id="imageContent9b3dafe3a0fd412b8bd9aebf23f6f8c0">
</div>
<p>Salford is set to be at the forefront of a national health revolution that will bring home care, mental health and community nursing, hospital and out-of-hospital services together, ushering in a new era of joined-up care. </p>
<p>The NHS announcement that the Salford Together Partnership – an alliance formed by NHS Salford Commissioning Group, Salford City Council, Salford Royal NHS Foundation Trust and Greater Manchester West Foundation Trust – is to become a ‘vanguard’ will lead to significant health improvements for residents.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.srft.nhs.uk/media-centre/latest-news/news-archive/news-2015/vanguard/" target="_self" title="read the full story">Read more...</a></p>
<p class="last-updated">Last updated on 16 March 2015.</p>
<p class="btt-link"><a href="#org-title">Back to top</a></p>
